# ============================================
# PM-Brain: Public Mode (Default)
# ============================================
# This repo is configured for FULLY PUBLIC use - ideal for:
# - Building a public learning portfolio
# - Sharing your growth journey openly
# - Creating content for blogs or portfolios
# - Open source contribution
#
# Everything is tracked and visible:
# - Daily learning logs
# - Weekly/monthly reflections  
# - Growth portfolio
# - Self-assessments
# - All learning artifacts
# - Company context (sanitize sensitive data)
# - Research and active work
#
# ============================================
# SWITCHING MODES
# ============================================
# To switch to PRIVATE mode (personal learning only):
#   Option 1 (Interactive): bash 00-Meta/SETUP.sh
#   Option 2 (Manual): cat .gitignore.private >> .gitignore
#
# To switch to TEAM mode (share templates, keep personal logs private):
#   Option 1 (Interactive): bash 00-Meta/SETUP.sh
#   Option 2 (Manual): cat .gitignore.team >> .gitignore
#
# See 00-Meta/README.md or 00-Meta/MODE-SELECTION-GUIDE.md for details.
#
# ============================================

